===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abyen}}, {{m|enm|abien}}, {{m|enm|abiggen}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ābyċġan||to buy; pay for; buy off; requite; recompense; redeem; perform; execute}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*uzbugjaną}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|a|buy}}. Cognate with {{cog|got|𐌿𐍃𐌱𐌿𐌲𐌾𐌰𐌽|sc=Goth}}.<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=11}}</ref>

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|RP|US}} {{IPA|/əˈbaɪ/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|aɪ|lang=en}}

