# {{lb|en|transitive|archaic}} To pay as [[penalty]], to [[suffer]]. {{defdate|from 12th c.}}<ref name=SOED/>
#* {{quote-book|year=1590|author={{w|Edmund Spenser}}|title=The Faerie Queene|section=III.4|passage=Who dyes, the utmost dolor doth '''abye'''; / But who that lives is lefte to waile his losse {{...}}.}}
