# {{lb|en|intransitive|obsolete}} Endure; remain. {{defdate|14th-16th c.}}<ref name=SOED/>
#* {{quote-book|year=1590|author={{w|Edmund Spenser}}|title={{w|The Faerie Queene}}|volume=III|passage=Nought that wanteth rest can long '''aby'''.}}
